        next = {'A New Journey'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = 'This Mission is skippable. Should you skip it and obtain a higher rank, completing this mission will be different. See the notes at the end of the page.\nIf you choose not to skip this mission, check the Three Mage Gate page for details on your options.\n1. Accept the mission and make your way to Heavens Tower.\n2. Pass by Kupipi and on to the second floor. Speak to Zubaba who will give you the [Key Item] Charm of light.\n3. Next, you will need to get past the Three Mage Gate in ruins tower at (J-7) in East Sarutabaruta (this is the same tower as the Survival Guide Inner Horutoto Ruins warp).\n4. Pass the Three Mage Gate and continue on to the small room at (G-7).\n5. Check the Gate of Light for a cutscene.\n6. Return to Heavens Tower and speak to Zubaba to finish the mission.',
